high_descs: Pick up the potato from the counter
Open microwave, cook potato, remove potato from the microwave
Turn around, take left to sink
Place the potato in the right side of the sink
anns.task_desc: Cook the potato and place it in sink

high_descs: Turn left and move to the kitchen island.
Pick up the potato from the front right corner of the kitchen island.
Turn around and move towards the dishwasher and face the microwave.

Open the microwave door, place the potato on the plate, close the microwave door, turn on the microwave, turn off the microwave, open the microwave door, and pick up the potato from the plate and then close the microwave door.
Turn right and move towards the sink.
Place the potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved potato in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and head towards the counter with the bread.
Pick up the potato from the counter.
Turn around and head towards the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the potato in it, heat it up, and take the potato out of microwave.
Turn around and head towards the sink on your left.
Place the potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the heated potato in the sink.
